---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="border-t border-rule mt-[120px] max-md:mt-[80px]">
  <div class="max-w-shell mx-auto px-14 max-md:px-6 py-14">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 max-md:grid-cols-1 gap-18 max-md:gap-12">
      <div>
        <div class="font-display text-[28px] leading-tight tracking-tightest">Waheng Note</div>
        <p class="text-fg-2 text-sm leading-relaxed mt-3 max-w-[40ch]">
          關於程式、工藝與機器的筆記 —— 持續寫能撐過週末之後的作品。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-fg-3">
        <div>
          <div class="text-fg-2 mb-3">導覽</div>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li><a href={base} class="hover:text-accent">首頁</a></li>
            <li><a href={`${base}blog/`} class="hover:text-accent">筆記</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-fg-2 mb-3">其他</div>
          <ul class="space-y-2">
            <li><a href="https://github.com/wahengchang" class="hover:text-accent">GitHub</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://wahengchang.github.io/ai-study-note/" class="hover:text-accent">Live site</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-14 pt-6 border-t border-rule font-mono text-[11px] text-fg-3 flex items-center justify-between">
      <span>© {year} Waheng</span>
      <span>Built with Astro 6 · Tailwind 4</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
